Description:
report metric

Usage: report_metric [-help] [<pattern>]
                     [-format {html json excel text vivid}] [-id <string>]
                     [-names <string>] [-out_file <string>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<pattern>                                # Pattern to match (string, optional)
-format {html json excel text vivid}     # Output format (enum, optional)
-id <string>                             # IDs of metrics to report (multiple
                                         # IDs will produce a comparison, first
                                         # is gold) (string, optional)
-names <string>                          # List of names (wildcards supported)
                                         # (string, optional)
-out_file <string>                       # Target file name (string, optional)